name: Enchanted Martial Artist's Gi
description: ﻿Ryoku started with Karate, then chased after masteries in Tae Kwon Do, Tang Soo Do, Aikido, Muay Thai Kickboxing, Krav Maga, Kung Fu, Jujitsu, and even Ninjutsu. This gi has been worn since the beginning of that journey, and is only cleaned by stints of training under waterfalls.
